{"tid":1125976,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"立法會請翻譯","createTime":"2019-04-26T05:21:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T14:13:26.000Z","uid":228995,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6de411b705974fd2fc63ba61b5276f16df3e5759","tid":1125976,"uid":228995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T05:21:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n五皮幾一個月 + 約滿酬金<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.legco.gov.hk/general/chinese/sec/jobs/job20190426-to-c.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fgeneral%2Fchinese%2Fsec%2Fjobs%2Fjob20190426-to-c.pdf&d=fAF%2FER2cs4qp%2F6NYk0BreHHr90zhVRml9IH8Z62du0k%3D&h=c2a17e58\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.legco.gov.hk/general/chinese/sec/jobs/job20190426-to-c.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n立法會秘書處<br />\n翻譯主任<br />\n立法會秘書處現正招聘優秀人才出任翻譯及傳譯部翻譯主任。在立法會行政管理委員會的監督下，秘書處的使命是為立法會提供高效及專業的秘書服務、資料研究及行政支援、提高公眾對立法會事務的認識，以及確保提供處理市民申訴的有效途徑。<br />\n<br />\n薪酬<br />\n入職薪酬為每月55,705元，並按5個按年增薪額增至70,090元，另有為翻譯主任職級而設的每月現金津貼(現時的津貼額為每月1,155元)。成功受聘人士會按合約條款受聘，為期3年，倘完成服務期而工作表現良好，可獲續約，並會獲得一筆約滿酬金，其款額加上僱主在強制性公積金計劃下所作的供款，相等於合約期內所得底薪總額的15%。附帶福利包括有薪假期、醫療及牙科福利。<br />\n<br />\n入職條件<br />\n應徵者應：<br />\n(a)持有認可大學學位，以翻譯或與語文有關科目的學位較佳，或具備同等學歷；<br />\n(b)具備最少6年從事翻譯/傳譯工作的經驗；<br />\n(c)具備極佳的  中、英文講寫能力；及<br />\n(d)具備非常良好的分析、溝通及督導能力，並能獨立工作及承受工作壓力。"},{"pid":"1c0528ba059a9d08ad0d165a6df1323b89fedb67","tid":1125976,"uid":172556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T02:58:49.000Z","msg":"有無人有apply？"},{"pid":"d51d9d48cbc867f96d4f9238011793c6dfae9f80","tid":1125976,"uid":228995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c0528ba059a9d08ad0d165a6df1323b89fedb67","tid":1125976,"uid":172556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T02:58:49.000Z","msg":"有無人有apply？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T11:59:13.000Z","msg":"有消息？"},{"pid":"22d46aea82a6bdf70713b137199e70d717990324","tid":1125976,"uid":172556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d51d9d48cbc867f96d4f9238011793c6dfae9f80","tid":1125976,"uid":228995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c0528ba059a9d08ad0d165a6df1323b89fedb67","tid":1125976,"uid":172556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T02:58:49.000Z","msg":"有無人有apply？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T11:59:13.000Z","msg":"有消息？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T12:00:36.000Z","msg":"咩消息？"},{"pid":"f2a26ffc7e717fe649e2c1562ef4ab0963aa188a","tid":1125976,"uid":172556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T14:13:26.000Z","msg":"冇巴絲apply？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}